name: Fall Damage (Sai139)
description:
I am not sure what it is. I thought of "playable poem" but that sounds pretentious. I don't know.

I got inspired to make a game during that 1 hour that does not really exist when we end daylight saving. It took me more than one hour to make, but I wanted to make it all in one sitting. It was important to me to make it that way. I don't think I should explain what it's about, it's better to make your own interpretation. 

Headphones and full screen recommended! I hope it connects with you.
